<br />Just for other people that may read this thread, the constants used in this example are:
<br />
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">PPUCTRL&nbsp; &nbsp;= $2000<br />PPUMASK&nbsp; &nbsp;= $2001<br />PPUSCROLL = $2005<br /><br />PPUCTRL_NMI = %10000000<br /></div></div>

